				<div class="hvres-meaning small">• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Do%C3%A3n-Khu%C3%AA/Canh-Tu%E1%BA%A5t-ni%C3%AAn-ch%E1%BA%BF/poem-x1HY9Hmqz-E6-xMz9JnWwA">Canh Tuất niên chế - 庚戌年製</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Do%C3%A3n-Khu%C3%AA/author-ueZqmqDIif0v3prANC9aXg">Doãn Khuê</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/Ch%C3%AD-h%E1%BA%ADu/poem-GWfYJr-9IbzhAgsP17PhdQ">Chí hậu - 至後</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/author-Se3x2jWTezvoDpkpSU9qjg">Đỗ Phủ</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Kh%E1%BB%95ng-T%E1%BB%AD/%C4%90%C3%B4ng-m%C3%B4n-chi-ph%E1%BA%A7n-3/poem-51oA6JBwB1Y2lhck6igdWg">Đông môn chi phần 3 - 東門之枌 3</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Kh%E1%BB%95ng-T%E1%BB%AD/author-Ghtg3UHpaIYXCkHiqunT7w">Khổng Tử</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-Khuy%E1%BA%BFn/Hung-ni%C3%AAn-k%E1%BB%B3-5/poem-YS7vBOFjdWE7oFgjTPJfLQ">Hung niên kỳ 5 - 凶年其五</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-Khuy%E1%BA%BFn/author-JHbQVfC53E2lRJL-xE616A">Nguyễn Khuyến</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/S%E1%BA%A7m-Tham/M%E1%BB%99-xu%C3%A2n-Qu%E1%BA%AFc-Ch%C3%A2u-%C4%91%C3%B4ng-%C4%91%C3%ACnh-t%E1%BB%91ng-L%C3%BD-T%C6%B0-M%C3%A3-quy-Ph%C3%B9-Phong-bi%E1%BB%87t-l%C6%B0/poem-Ev5JnJZsluhtpec8dzAk9A">Mộ xuân Quắc Châu đông đình tống Lý Tư Mã quy Phù Phong biệt lư - 暮春虢州東亭送李司馬歸扶風別廬</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/S%E1%BA%A7m-Tham/author-AcWs16LhWAEAw513Kk2DnA">Sầm Tham</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Tr%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-K%E1%BA%BF/S%C6%A1n-gia/poem-fp--g4IQL8JEqMl-bSxUAQ">Sơn gia - 山家</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Tr%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-K%E1%BA%BF/author-sfmhVlf4_IkoZCtK-3Bc5g">Trương Kế</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/T%E1%BA%A3-ho%C3%A0i-k%E1%BB%B3-1/poem-i6J_gjKNUJ7zwhSthu0ADQ">Tả hoài kỳ 1 - 寫懷其一</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/author-Se3x2jWTezvoDpkpSU9qjg">Đỗ Phủ</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Kh%E1%BB%95ng-T%E1%BB%AD/Thi%C3%AAn-b%E1%BA%A3o-2/poem-m8MohZNqnRFP5rWqJ4_dsA">Thiên bảo 2 - 天保 2</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Kh%E1%BB%95ng-T%E1%BB%AD/author-Ghtg3UHpaIYXCkHiqunT7w">Khổng Tử</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/H%E1%BB%A9a-H%E1%BB%93n/Th%C3%ADnh-x%C6%B0%E1%BB%9Bng-S%C6%A1n-gi%C3%A1-c%C3%B4/poem-2JC7DQc8l_C-Q7IUyCMJag">Thính xướng “Sơn giá cô” - 聽唱山鷓鴣</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/H%E1%BB%A9a-H%E1%BB%93n/author-67u8r1Npo8IzUDBZnVHSFA">Hứa Hồn</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/B%E1%BB%93-%C4%90%E1%BA%A1o-Nguy%C3%AAn/T%E1%BB%AB-Thi%E1%BB%83m-T%C3%A2y-Nho-h%E1%BB%8Dc-%C4%91%E1%BB%81-c%E1%BB%AD-nh%C3%A0n-c%C6%B0-ng%C3%B4n-ch%C3%AD/poem-PSR1uQO_UnVPoC0A-ZZX9g">Từ Thiểm Tây Nho học đề cử nhàn cư ngôn chí - 辭陝西儒學提舉閒居言志</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/B%E1%BB%93-%C4%90%E1%BA%A1o-Nguy%C3%AAn/author-vNqjO3qn_lddcLSXVQdpGA">Bồ Đạo Nguyên</a>)<br/></div>	</div>
